data.description: This beautiful, historic home is ready for its’ new owner! Step inside and take in the beautiful hardwood floors, neutral paint colors, and crown molding throughout the home. The kitchen has been gutted and redone and the white shutters and built-in bookshelves make each room feel warm and cozy. Ample amount of storage and counter space in the kitchen complete with all stainless steel appliances. Turn the extra rooms into an office, craft room, or even a music room. Enjoy the lovely spacious sun room, where french doors lead out to the wonderful wood deck, great for hosting gatherings and celebrations.  Besides the kitchen being redone with new cabinets, there is a new 20’ x 40’ two car garage, new roof in 2020, brand new custom front door, refurnished stairs, all appliances under two years old, brand new fencing with automatic gate. NEVER FLOODED! Home is owner occupied please schedule 12 hr in advance. Make this home yours for the holidays!
